<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="KR5c0124-zh-e9d89248" type="transl"><teiHeader><fileDesc><titleStmt><title>列子古注新譯</title><editor role="translator">Xiao Dengfu 蕭登福</editor></titleStmt><publicationStmt><ab>published electronically as part of the TLS project at https://hxwd.org</ab><availability status="4">The copyright status of this work is unclear</availability></publicationStmt><sourceDesc><bibl><title>列子古注新譯</title>臺北：文津出版社，1990</bibl><ab>Translation of <bibl corresp="#KR5c0124"><title xml:lang="och">列子</title></bibl> into <lang xml:lang="zh">Chinese</lang>.</ab></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><creation resp="#CH">Initially created: <date>2023-11-20T22:57:32.792+09:00</date> by CH</creation></profileDesc></teiHeader><text><body><div><head>Translated parts</head><p xml:id="KR5c0124-start"><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T01:33:41.76+09:00">列子居住在鄭國的國田，</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T01:34:09.613+09:00">已經有四十年了。鄭圖上下沒有一個人能認識列子的才幹o</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T01:34:35.327+09:00">圖君跟卿大夫都把他看做</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T01:34:53.04+09:00">像普通百姓一樣。</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T01:35:27.233+09:00">有一年鄭國饑荒，</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T01:36:08.396+09:00">列子將離家前往衛國避饑荒。</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T01:36:30.093+09:00">他的學生對他說:</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T01:37:16.388+09:00">「老師這一去不知什麼時候才會再回來。</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T01:38:18.344+09:00">學生大臆想向老師請求教誨，</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T01:38:50.509+09:00">不知老師將教我什麼?</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T01:40:05.76+09:00">老師是否有從太老師壺丘子林那邊聽到特殊的言論呢?」</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T01:43:33.051+09:00">列子笑著說••</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T01:43:56.847+09:00">「壺丘先生哪裡曾向我講過什麼特殊的話呢!</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T01:44:42.817+09:00">雖然如此，</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T01:46:23.264+09:00">我的老師壺丘先生會告訴過我的同學伯昏完人，</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T01:47:50.368+09:00">我在旁邊聽到了，</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T01:48:20.136+09:00">我嘗試著把他的話告訴你。</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T01:48:33.185+09:00">他說:</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T01:49:26.633+09:00">能創生萬物的東西(道)，它的自體不是因創生而來的。</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T01:57:09.178+09:00">能變化萬物的東西(道)，它是不受其他變化所改變的。</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.23" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T01:57:26.067+09:00">不因創生而來的東西，才能創生萬物;</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.24" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T01:57:38.568+09:00">不受其他變化所改變的東西，才能變化萬物。</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.25" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T02:03:30.444+09:00">能創生萬物者，它不能不創生萬物;</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.26" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T02:04:26.225+09:00">能變化萬物者，它不能不變化萬物;這一切的生化現象，都是由不得已，不得不如此，</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.27" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T02:04:04.217+09:00">所以萬物永遠都在生誠變化之中0</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.28" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T02:04:35.666+09:00">萬物永遠都在生激變化，</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.29" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T02:07:13.448+09:00">是說萬物無時無刻無不是</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.31" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T02:07:42.648+09:00">不僅小的事物如此，連充鑫於天地的陰陽氣，</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.30" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T02:07:36.422+09:00">都在生誠變化之中的。</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.32" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T02:08:22.77+09:00">以及春夏秋冬四季的運轉，也都是如此。</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.33" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T02:08:40.595+09:00">不因創生而來的道體，它像是獨立於萬物之上(疑獨);</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.34" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T02:09:31.452+09:00">不受變化的道體，它能使萬物往來代謝，。</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.35" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T02:13:01.247+09:00">隨時變化(往復)道體能使萬物代謝往來，</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.36" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T02:13:21.876+09:00">所以它是無邊際的。</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.38" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T02:12:41.955+09:00">所以它是無法加以窮究的。</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.37" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T02:12:57.537+09:00">道體像是獨立於萬物之上，</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.39" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T02:13:28.657+09:00">《黃一帝書》曾說••</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.40" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T02:16:26.611+09:00">「至虛無物(谷)神奇奧妙(神)的道體，它是沒有生滅現象的，</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.41" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T02:16:53.748+09:00">它是玄妙的創生萬物者(玄舵，枕能生物)。</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.42" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T02:17:03.045+09:00">在玄妙的創生者(道)之處，它像是門戶，</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.43" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T02:17:28.662+09:00">使天地萬物生滅往來，因此它也可以說是天地的根源。</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.44" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T02:17:43.098+09:00">它看起來，極其徵細，像是有物，像無物，</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.45" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T02:19:29.344+09:00">但它在造化萬物時，卻能夠源跟不絕。』</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.46" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T02:20:00.3+09:00">所以說能創生萬物變化萬物的道體，它不是被創生，</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.47" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T02:20:18.39+09:00">也不會隨物而變化的。</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.48" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T02:20:34.715+09:00">而道體的生化萬物，與萬物的被生化，</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.49" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T02:21:37.744+09:00">都是自然而然，自己自然起創生，自然有變化，自己自然而有形體容色，</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.50" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T02:22:26.966+09:00">自然而有智慧、能力，</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.51" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T02:22:40.467+09:00">得失成敗。這一切生化現象都是自然而然，不得不然的。</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-1a.52" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T02:22:56.213+09:00">我們如果說••有一個東西在主宰這一切的生法、變化、形體、容色、智慧、能力、得失、成敗，</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_001-2a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-22T02:22:57.159+09:00">那我們便錯了。」</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.40" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-09T10:07:41.714+09:00">列子說:</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.41" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-09T10:07:55.228+09:00">「一個已懂得真意的人，是不必用言語來做解說的。</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.42" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-09T10:08:09.158+09:00">一個極盡聰明智慧的人，是不必借由語言文字才能了解的。</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.43" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-09T10:08:20.513+09:00">以無言的方式來傳達道體，也是一種表達的方式。</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.44" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-09T10:08:31.3+09:00">以無知之智(不以世俗之智)來了悟道理，也是一種知道的方式。</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.45" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-09T10:14:47.774+09:00">因此能體悟道體是無言者，便能不必有所言說(无言與不言);</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.46" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-09T10:22:17.769+09:00">能體悟道體是無知者，便能不以世智來知曉(完知與不知;道離言語覺知，无言无知)。而无言、不言;无知、不知，</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.47" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-09T10:22:25.77+09:00">也算是言，也算是知。</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.48" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-09T10:22:37.297+09:00">正因為悟道者是无言无知;</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.49" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-09T10:23:29.55+09:00">所以能無所不言，無所不知。</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.52" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-09T10:25:29.228+09:00">看起來像土偶人;</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.50" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-09T10:24:55.546+09:00">也正為悟道者常現出不言，不知;所以是无所言，</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.51" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-09T10:25:03.633+09:00">無所知，</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-6a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-09T10:25:56.484+09:00">南郭子也是像這樣子罷了，你們又何必隨便妄加驚駭呢</seg></p></div></body></text></TEI>